==English==

===Alternative spellings===
*case-sensitive

===Adjective===
'''[[case]] [[sensitive]]'''
#Distinguishing [[uppercase|upper-]] and [[lowercase|lower-case]] letters.  Often used in computer science to indicate a distinction is made in comparison or equality of letters based on [[case]].  For example, a case-sensitive password will not recognize "Password" and "password" as the same, but a [[case insensitive]] comparison would.

